{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"背景\"><a href=\"#%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>背景</h2>\n<p>在一次开发过程中，对一个元素设置CSS <code class=\"language-text\">overflow-x: hidden;</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">overflow-y: visible;</code> ，理想状况下，在X轴超出部分隐藏，Y轴超出部分显示。然而，元素属性并没有生效。</p>\n<h2 id=\"原因\"><a href=\"#%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>原因</h2>\n<p>根据<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css3-box/##overflow-x\">W3C</a>的说法，如下</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The computed values of ‘overflow-x’ and ‘overflow-y’ are the same as their specified values, except that some combinations with ‘visible’ are not possible: if one is specified as ‘visible’ and the other is ‘scroll’ or ‘auto’, then ‘visible’ is set to ‘auto’. The computed value of ‘overflow’ is equal to the computed value of ‘overflow-x’ if ‘overflow-y’ is the same; otherwise it is the pair of computed values of ‘overflow-x’ and ‘overflow-y’. </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>也就是说，如果同一个元素X,Y轴上，其中一个设置了<code class=\"language-text\">visible</code>，例外一个设置了<code class=\"language-text\">scoll</code>或者<code class=\"language-text\">auto</code>，这时候，<code class=\"language-text\">visible</code>属性自动转变为<code class=\"language-text\">auto</code>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"解决方法\"><a href=\"#%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>解决方法</h2>\n<p>在目标属性外，嵌套父层，一个设置<code class=\"language-text\">overflow-x: hidden;</code>另外一个设置， <code class=\"language-text\">overflow-y: visible;</code> 即可。</p>\n<h2 id=\"参考链接\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>参考链接</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/6421966/css-overflow-x-visible-and-overflow-y-hidden-causing-scrollbar-issue\">http://stackoverflow.com/questions/6421966/css-overflow-x-visible-and-overflow-y-hidden-causing-scrollbar-issue</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.brunildo.org/test/Overflowxy2.html\">http://www.brunildo.org/test/Overflowxy2.html</a></li>\n</ol>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"背景 在一次开发过程中，对一个元素设置CSS   and   ，理想状况下，在X轴超出部分隐藏，Y轴超出部分显示。然而，元素属性并没有生